02:34.100 --> 02:35.567
This year, I'm hot.

02:35.567 --> 02:37.868
See, in the past, I haven't
been interested in girls.

02:37.868 --> 02:42.234
Seeing Kelly in the morning
can do that to a guy.

02:44.100 --> 02:47.033
No, but this year,
I threw around a few winks,

02:47.033 --> 02:49.868
let it be known
I'm accepting Valentines,

02:49.868 --> 02:51.868
so they should be rolling in.

02:51.868 --> 02:53.367
Won't they, Mom?

02:53.367 --> 02:56.367
Sure, they will, son.

02:56.367 --> 02:57.901
But not for you.

02:57.901 --> 03:01.300
Well, I'm
off to the mall.

03:01.300 --> 03:02.868
Hey, Kel,
I see you're wearing

03:02.868 --> 03:04.467
your "love me for my mind"
outfit again.

03:08.501 --> 03:11.000
