those two awful children,

08:13.801 --> 08:16.701
and he can't even
tell you he loves you?

08:16.701 --> 08:18.300
I've heard him say
"I love the Cubs."

08:18.300 --> 08:19.300
"I'd love a beer."

08:19.300 --> 08:21.834
"I'd love it
if you leave, Marcie."

08:21.834 --> 08:22.868
Face it, Peggy.

08:22.868 --> 08:25.100
This man's no stranger
to the word "love."

08:25.100 --> 08:28.567
Oh, it doesn't matter.
I mean, I know he loves me.

08:28.567 --> 08:30.067
He doesn't say it,

08:30.067 --> 08:33.067
