08:34.567 --> 08:36.967
I mean, he does so many other
wonderful things for me.

08:36.967 --> 08:40.534
He, uh...

08:42.100 --> 08:43.701
Hi, Mom.

08:43.701 --> 08:46.868
Kelly, what does
your father do for me?

08:46.868 --> 08:51.267
Well, he...

08:51.267 --> 08:53.000
Daddy?

08:53.000 --> 08:54.100
Nevermind.

08:54.100 --> 08:55.601
Where's your brother?

08:55.601 --> 08:57.133
Oh, he's standing
by the mailbox,

08:57.133 --> 08:58.601
waiting for a valentine.

08:58.601 --> 09:00.100
I haven't got the heart

09:00.100 --> 09:02.100
