it's Sunday.

09:02.100 --> 09:04.634
Well, just in case he doesn't
get one this year,

09:04.634 --> 09:06.868
I want you to
go easy on him, okay?

09:06.868 --> 09:08.267
Come on, Mom.
We both know

09:08.267 --> 09:10.100
that Bud's an obnoxious,
ratlike creature,

09:10.100 --> 09:13.133
but it doesn't mean
I don't love him.

09:13.133 --> 09:14.267
He knows that.

09:14.267 --> 09:15.801
How does he know that?

09:15.801 --> 09:16.734
I tell him.

09:17.868 --> 09:20.167
Well, has
he ever told you?

09:20.167 --> 09:21.367
Oh, sure. You got to.

09:21.367 --> 09:22.968
I mean, it kind of
takes the edge

09:22.968 --> 09:24.734
off things like this...

09:30.133 --> 09:32.467
Oh, Bud. It's Sunday.

09:32.467 --> 09:35.634
There's no mail
on Sunday.

09:35.634 --> 09:37.968
Happy Valentine's Day.

09:37.968 --> 09:42.300
No!

09:42.300 --> 09:45.968
Love him? You betcha.

09:45.968 --> 09:48.501
Hey, Peg. How come when I said,
"Hi, Bud,"

09:48.501 --> 09:50.701
