"I don't need your pity"?

09:53.000 --> 09:54.534
You don't really want to know,
do you?

09:54.534 --> 09:57.968
Nope.

09:57.968 --> 10:03.133
What time is dinner
rearing its ugly head?

10:03.133 --> 10:04.968
Soon, honey.

10:04.968 --> 10:08.133
By the way...
I love you, Al.

10:08.133 --> 10:11.434
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

10:11.434 --> 10:13.968
Look, Peg, I know you're
anxiously awaiting

10:13.968 --> 10:17.400
